ve alerts every %(days)s concerning\r\n  recommendations in the following fields published on the\r\n  <i>%(applongname)s</i> web site: %(thematics)s.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n  Finally, if you are interested in becoming a recommender for\r\n  <i>%(appname)s</i> -\r\n  <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2BDrPoHGkn0">see video</a> - please\r\n  contact a current recommender in your field via this link\r\n  <a href="%(recommurl)s">%(recommurl)s</a>.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Thanks again for your interest and for joining <i>%(applongname)s</i>.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n  Yours sincerely,\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n  The Managing Board of <i>%(applongname)s</i>\r\n</p>\r\n
